core.model.management

Class AbstractModelManager<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.model.management.AbstractModelManager<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of the model to manage.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    IModelManager<E>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractStatefulModelManager

    public abstract class AbstractModelManager<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IModelManager<E>
    an AbstractModelManager generic abstract class that is used to factor the common interface and state of all concrete model manager classes.

    It must be specialized by all concrete model manager classes.
    Author:
    Bachar Rima

        public AbstractModelManager(java.lang.String path)
        Creates a model manager to manage the model associated to a specific path. The importation details of the model associated to the path will be explicited in the constructors of the concrete implementations of this class.
        Parameters:
        path - the path associated to the model to be managed by this model manager
